Package: econimap
Title: Analyst-Facing MMM Workflow Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Matt", "Price", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "matt@example.com")
Author: Matt Price [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Matt Price <matt@example.com>
Description: A script-compatible MMM workflow toolkit for hierarchical Stan MMM,
    quasi-geo evidence, response curves, scenario planning, and deck-ready outputs.
    The package shell keeps the current analyst scripts available while providing
    a cleaner installation and loading surface.
